  "title": "TCM Physician",
  "description": "<p>We are hiring TRADITIONAL CHINESE MEDICINE PRACTITIONER for our Traditional Chinese Medicine clinic. We welcome all races but being able to read Chinese is a must as our medical records are all in Chinese. And being able to speak Mandarin is a requirement too as most of our customers are elderly Chinese who can only speak Mandarin or dialect. Being able to converse in and write simple English is a must too as we also have non-Chinese customers . Conversant in Dialect would be a please</p><p>工作内容： •新加坡注册中医师• 精通华文，能够以简单的英文沟通及书写，能以方言沟通更为理想。 • 无需相关学历或经验。 • 性格友善，善于沟通，勤奋好学。 若有兴趣，请Whatsapp 83896656. Thank you</p>",
